{
  "texts": [
    "Generative Agents [20] and AgentSims [34] construct multiple agents in a virtual town to simulate the human daily life.",
    "SocialAI School [109] employs LLM-based agents to simulate and investigate the fundamental social cognitive skills during the course of child development.",
    "S 3 [77] builds a social network simulator, focusing on the propagation of information, emotion and attitude.",
    "CGMI [111] is a framework for multi-agent simulation.",
    "CGMI maintains the personality of the agents through a tree structure and constructs a cognitive model."
  ]
}